INSERT INTO `jos_jf_content` VALUES ('468', '3', '101', 'content', 'introtext', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong></strong></span></span></span><strong></strong></span><strong></strong></p><p> Y <span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">  es, gibt es oft Kinder hier, und sie scheinen es zu genießen Urlaub mehr als Eltern.  Ihre Kinder können spielen hier in einer sehr sicheren Umgebung einschließlich entdecken viele der Inseln Überraschungen. </span></p>', '973a637929dd3e5c835c066a0c3fc464', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\"><strong></strong></span></span></span><strong></strong></span><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p>Y<span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">es, there are often children here and they seem to enjoy there vacation more than there parents. Your children can safely play here in a very safe environment including discovering many of the Islands surprises.</span></p>', '2009-01-07 21:14:35', '62', '1');
