\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">10. Disputes You and LRA agree that any disputes arising from your use of this web site will be subject to Venezuelan law and the non-exclusive jurisdiction of the Ve courts.</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">11. LRA reserves the right to change or amend these web site terms and conditions without prior notice.</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">12. LRA is not responsible for content being reproduced on this website or information being published by third persons or material sent to us or updated automatically by online users or members of the Venezuela Travel 2.0 community under the open source regulations.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">13. LRA have no responsibility for text or photos being published by users and providers of the web 2.0 interface.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: #000000; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">Legal notices: Privacy Policy</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">At LRA, we recognize the sensitive nature of your personal and business information. For your protection, all information transmitted by you to us while visiting this website is secured using the latest technology in software encryption and security. <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">LRA provides this privacy policy in order to demonstrate our firm commitment to Internet privacy and to make you aware of our privacy practices, and of the choices you can make about the way your personal and business information is collected and used by LRA.</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">What information does this site and LRA monitor</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">When you browse the site, we do not collect personal information about you. The only way we will get any kind of personal information is if you give it to us. The company requires that consumers supply personal information, including e-mail addresses and Telephone Numbers, during the booking process. On occasion the company also collects additional personal information from subscribers in an optional e-mail subscription form. Demographic information provided by a subscriber may be combined with site usage reports to profile, in aggregate form, users and their preferences in site content and advertising. The company employs cookies to measure site usage and related information. If you are making a booking we may also use cookies to keep track of the transaction from one page to the next. We use third-party advertising companies (such as www.google.com) to serve ads on other web sites. These companies may use cookie-based information (not including your name, address email address or telephone number) about your visits to this and other web sites in order to measure advertising effectiveness. We may also collect information about your visit to our web site, based on your browsing (click stream) activities. This information may include the pages you browse and products and services viewed or booked for example. This helps us to better manage and develop our offers and to provide you with better products and services tailored to your individual interests and needs.</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">What does LRA do with the information it gathers</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">We may use this information to measure the entry and exit points of visitors to the site and respective numbers of visitors to various pages and sections of the site and details of searches performed. We may also use this information to measure the usage of advertising banners, other click troughs from the site. We may disclose information of this nature in aggregate form to third parties, personal information on individual visitors will not be passed on to any third party. Users who have subscribed to our e-mail service or visitors purchasing products on the site that have not opted out; will receive promotional mailings and e-mails from LRA. Your personal details will not be passed to any other third parties except where necessary to process your booking or enquiry. Your details may be passed to countries outside of the European Economic Area in order to process and arrange for the products and services you request. When you submit your booking or request to us you agree that we may use and transfer your personal information in this manner. LRA will provide a summary of any personal information held upon request. This information will only be sent to the e-mail address on file for the subscriber name associated with it. </span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">To obtain information summary please e-mail: reservation</span><a href=\"mailto:mail@yachtcharter.travel\"><span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">@losroques-airlines.com</span></span></a><span style=\"color: #000000;\">.</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Links to other sites LRA, its contractors, travel agents, owners, and employees are not responsible for the content or the privacy policies of web sites to which it may link.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">Legal notices: security statement This Web site takes every precaution to protect our users information. When users submit sensitive information via the Web site, their information is protected both online and off-line.</span><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Tahoma;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #000000; font-family: Arial;\">Legal notices: Community information.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #888888;\">Registered office and address for legal service of documents:<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #888888; font-family: Arial;\">LRA : Counter 38 Terminal Auxilliar Maiquetia, Venezuela.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #888888; font-family: Arial;\">reservation</span><a href=\"mailto:mail@yachtcharter.travel\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #888888; font-family: Arial;\">@losroques-airlines.com</span></span></a></p>', '2009-01-14 16:39:32', '62', '1');
